name: Chilly Rodriguez
description:
- Animated wall #4 -
Chilly Rodriguez knows how to enjoy the moment.
I painted this relaxing buddy quite some time ago in Buenos Aires, Argentina, spring 2012. Now I fixed some details and added some digital animation to give him more life.
Sadly this wall doesn’t exist anymore. Not the painting, not even the wall itself. They threw it down and replace it with a "cool building". Anyways, maybe you can find it in older versions of Google Maps. Here’re the coordinates:
34°33'54.1"S 58°28'51.5"W
 https://goo.gl/maps/WZrvVkqGq17XTFYT7
